{"tid":1988941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[造勢DQ]文匯、大公、星島、01 社評齊轟郭榮鏗　大公：不見棺材不流淚","createTime":"2020-04-25T14:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T17:26:46.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"630cfb0c8d549ead7a68847cbf4cafae949ab3d2","tid":1988941,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"立場報道<br />\n<br />\n立法會內務委員會昨日（24日）舉行第 16 次會議，仍未選出主席。今日多份親中及親建制報章刊登社評批評內會主持郭榮鏗，其中《文匯報》炮轟郭榮鏗言行「囂張跋扈」，明顯觸犯《基本法》第 104 條有關宣誓的規定，必須承擔相應法律責任；《大公報》則指郭主持下的內會停擺 6 個月，明顯是違反「公職人員行為失當」的證據。《大公報》又指，反對派企圖在換屆選舉中進一步控制立法會，實現奪權「三部曲」，將會導致香港百業蕭條、民不聊生，「又豈是絕大多數市民之福？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%A7%E6%9C%83%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF-%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC-%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-01-%E7%A4%BE%E8%A9%95%E9%BD%8A%E8%BD%9F%E9%83%AD%E6%A6%AE%E9%8F%97-%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%8B%E6%A3%BA%E6%9D%90%E4%B8%8D%E6%B5%81%E6%B7%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B3%25B6-01-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A9%2595%25E9%25BD%258A%25E8%25BD%259F%25E9%2583%25AD%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E9%258F%2597-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%25A3%25BA%25E6%259D%2590%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%25B7%259A%2F&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKuaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=a8e09db4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B3%25B6-01-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A9%2595%25E9%25BD%258A%25E8%25BD%259F%25E9%2583%25AD%25E6%25A6%25AE%25E9%258F%2597-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%25A3%25BA%25E6%259D%2590%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%25B7%259A%2F&h=1a2a0